<br>
/tar person<br>
/assist<br>
/i am killing a %T<br>
/e blah blah balh %T<br>
<br>
To this:<br>
<br>
/assist person<br>
/i am killing a %T<br>
/e blah blah balh %T<br>
<br>
Or even:<br>
<br>
/ass person<br>
/i am killing a %T<br>
/e blah blah balh %T<br>
<br>
Hope that helps you some.<br>
